      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/15/133",
      "text": [
        " «يُجْزِيهِ أَنْ يَبُلَّهُ مِنْ بَعْضِ جَسَدِهِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.133 - Abu Al-Hasan Imam Musa ibn Jafar Al-Kadhim (as) was asked about a man who, while performing wudu, misses a small area on his face that the water does not reach.\nImam (as) said: \"It suffices for him to moisten it with water from another part of his body.\""
        ]
      }
